Abstract: Michael Abram is charged with attempted murder in the stabbing of George Harrison in London and is sent to a prison mental clinic for evaluation (M)
Snippet: Michael Abram is charged with attempted murder in the stabbing of George Harrison in London and is sent to a prison mental clinic for evaluation (M)
LeadParagraph: The man accused of stabbing George Harrison on Thursday was charged with attempted murder today and then sent to a prison mental clinic for evaluation.

Headline.Main: Suspect in Beatle Attack Held in Psychiatric Unit
